 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"},{"pid":"1c4cb4381e040911d90399b9dacc0f02ea4e69a0","tid":1851404,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"睇住班支那廢老，笑左出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔識上網又資訊唔流通，食二手貨食假貨就係呢班，一話有就出去成班交叉感染。仲要肺炎死得多廢老，今次將人口大換血<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82032b7de73dfe75c0871d3b78ea6dac77b32b67","tid":1851404,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30